# Local Project Memory (Template)

Copy this file to `CLAUDE.local.md` for personal project preferences.
This file is automatically gitignored.

## Personal Preferences

- Prefer verbose test output: `pytest -v --tb=long`
- Use debug logging when running API

## Local Environment

```bash
# My local database
export DJ_AI_DATABASE_URL="sqlite+aiosqlite:///./dev.db"

# Yandex token (get from https://yandex-music.readthedocs.io/en/main/token.html)
export DJ_AI_YANDEX_TOKEN="your-token-here"
```

## Test Data

- Sample tracks in `~/Music/test-tracks/`
- Test BPM range: 120-140 for house, 140-160 for techno

## Notes

- API runs on http://localhost:8000
- Web app runs on http://localhost:3000
- MCP server connects via stdio
